title: BBC Football Focus 720p 50fps 16.09.2017
description:
Dan Walker, Mark Schwarzer and Alex Scott preview the weekend's Premier League action.  
 
Newcastle captain Jamaal Lascelles tells all about his team's fighting spirit and training ground bust-ups.  
 
There is also an interview with the Crystal Palace defender Pape Souare, who a year ago broke his thigh bone in a car crash but is now on the verge of returning to the first team.
